{
  "texts": [
    "This study aimed to develop a conceptual design framework that integrates TRIZ and EBD based on an LLM.",
    "The goal is to aid designers in effectively addressing design problems.",
    "The framework involves selecting and simulating various modules from each design methodology.",
    "An important question could be raised here: How and why was each module selected and then tailored together?",
    "The selection and adaptation of modules were based on two main criteria."
  ]
}